wooden skewer inserted into the centre of the cake comes out clean. Cool in tin for 5 minutes, then turn out onto a wire rack to cool completely."},{"content":"Dust cake with extra icing sugar and serve warm with whipped cream (optional)."}],"hintsAndTricks":["You can replace the rhubarb with seasonal stone fruit or fresh berries in this recipe, but cooking times may vary."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","35m","8 portions"]}